{"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/BindingGroupRef\/addToggleRef(notify:data:)"},"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"addToggleRef"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"notify"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"GToggleNotify","preciseIdentifier":"c:gobject.h@T@GToggleNotify","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"?, ","kind":"text"},{"text":"data","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:gtypes.h@T@gpointer","text":"gpointer","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"? = nil)"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This functionality is intended for binding ","type":"text"},{"code":"object","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to a proxy"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object managed by another memory manager. This is done with two"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"paired references: the strong reference added by","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_add_toggle_ref()"},{"text":" and a reverse reference to the proxy","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"object which is either a strong reference or weak reference."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The setup is that when there are no other references to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"object"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"only a weak reference is held in the reverse direction from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"object"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to the proxy object, but when there are other references held to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"object"},{"text":", a strong reference is held. The ","type":"text"},{"code":"notify","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" callback is called","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"when the reference from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"object"},{"text":" to the proxy object should be","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"“toggled” from strong to weak (","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"is_last_ref"},{"text":" true) or weak to strong","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"("},{"code":"is_last_ref","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" false)."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Since a (normal) reference must be held to the object before"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"calling "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_add_toggle_ref()"},{"text":", the initial state of the reverse","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"link is always strong.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Multiple toggle references may be added to the same gobject,","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"however if there are multiple toggle references to an object, none"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"of them will ever be notified until all but one are removed.  For"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"this reason, you should only ever use a toggle reference if there","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"is important state in the proxy object."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Note that if you unref the object on another thread, then ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notify"},{"type":"text","text":" might"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"still be invoked after ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_object_remove_toggle_ref()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", and the object argument","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"might be a dangling pointer. If the object is destroyed on other threads,"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"you must take care of that yourself.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_add_toggle_ref()"},{"type":"text","text":" must be released with "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_remove_toggle_ref()"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/glibobject\/bindinggroupref\/addtoggleref(notify:data:)"]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject","doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/BindingGroupRef","doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/BindingGroupRef\/ObjectProtocol-Implementations"]]},"abstract":[{"text":"Increases the reference count of the object by one and sets a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"callback to be called when all other references to the object are"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"dropped, or when this is already the last reference to the object","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and another reference is established."}],"sections":[],"metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"addToggleRef"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"notify"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"GToggleNotify","preciseIdentifier":"c:gobject.h@T@GToggleNotify","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"?, ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"data"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:gtypes.h@T@gpointer","text":"gpointer","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"?)"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","modules":[{"name":"GLibObject"}],"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method","title":"addToggleRef(notify:data:)","externalID":"s:10GLibObject0B8ProtocolPAAE12addToggleRef6notify4datayySvSg_SpySo8_GObjectVGSgs5Int32VtXCSg_AGtF::SYNTHESIZED::s:10GLibObject15BindingGroupRefV","extendedModule":"GLibObject"},"references":{"doc://GLibObject/documentation/GLibObject":{"role":"collection","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject","abstract":[],"title":"GLibObject","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/glibobject"},"doc://GLibObject/documentation/GLibObject/BindingGroupRef":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"BindingGroupRef"}],"title":"BindingGroupRef","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"BindingGroupRef"}],"type":"topic","abstract":[{"code":"GBindingGroup","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" can be used to bind multiple properties"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"from an object collectively.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/BindingGroupRef","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/glibobject\/bindinggroupref"},"doc://GLibObject/documentation/GLibObject/BindingGroupRef/ObjectProtocol-Implementations":{"title":"ObjectProtocol Implementations","type":"topic","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/BindingGroupRef\/ObjectProtocol-Implementations","role":"collectionGroup","url":"\/documentation\/glibobject\/bindinggroupref\/objectprotocol-implementations","kind":"article"},"doc://GLibObject/documentation/GLibObject/BindingGroupRef/addToggleRef(notify:data:)":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/BindingGroupRef\/addToggleRef(notify:data:)","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"addToggleRef","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"notify","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"GToggleNotify","preciseIdentifier":"c:gobject.h@T@GToggleNotify"},{"text":"?, ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"data"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:gtypes.h@T@gpointer","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"gpointer"},{"text":"?)","kind":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/glibobject\/bindinggroupref\/addtoggleref(notify:data:)","abstract":[{"text":"Increases the reference count of the object by one and sets a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"callback to be called when all other references to the object are"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"dropped, or when this is already the last reference to the object","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and another reference is established.","type":"text"}],"title":"addToggleRef(notify:data:)","role":"symbol"}}}